{"tid":929144,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"當年既A米同挪威小神童宜家連包皮既車尾燈都見唔到","createTime":"2018-12-05T11:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T12:28:05.000Z","uid":46013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc66ee50d8ff8f0a6c590a3c1fd6f0fc4fa6b55","tid":929144,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"依兩件當年俾人吹到幾勁幾勁 <br />\nA米果件直程未夠秤就話要升上一隊救亡 宜家要去希臘既不知名球隊踢大後備 <br />\n奥迪加特還好 起碼係維迪斯都有正正常常既表現同出場時間 但皇馬好似無意用番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同年出世既包皮 細個一直無咩新聞 歐聯踢贏曼城之後 身價直升幾百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要被提名金球獎 尋日仲拎埋 Kopa<br />\n<br />\n基利安&middot;麥巴比（Kylian Mbapp&eacute; Lottin，1998年12月20日<br />\n哈基姆&middot;馬斯圖爾（Hachim Mastour，阿拉伯語：هاشم مستور&lrm;，轉寫：Hāshim Mastūr，1998年6月15日－）<br />\nNorwegian footballer<br />\n馬丁&middot;奧德加特（Martin &Oslash;degaard，1998年12月17日－）是一位挪威足球運動員"},{"pid":"f8ef1d69b31b5dc759a3549758865de6c8000a63","tid":929144,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞個件呢？"},{"pid":"986929e4b5bda7367d5de2361ca04de7f4d6392a","tid":929144,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8ef1d69b31b5dc759a3549758865de6c8000a63","tid":929144,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞個件呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"哈里奴域? 大過佢地2年 宜家不受A米重用"},{"pid":"7bd76bab6f6237385b42c2b94701ecfe34866f67","tid":929144,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1abb26c611baf1bf301c3c11